Usually I hate it when APIs break. TMF 0.8 introduces a different scoping API than Xtext 0.7. It took me a while to figure out. So I&#8217;ll show the changes below: Component : "component" name = ID "{" (ports+=Port)* "}";
Port : "port" dir=Direction name=ID ":" ref=[Interface&#124;ID] ";" ;
enum Direction : IN="in" &#124; OUT="out";
Instance: "instance" name=ID ":" [...]
